1014
01:19:56,173 --> 01:19:58,498
我们不知道我们有多少人还活着
We don't know how many of our people are still alive.

1015
01:19:58,676 --> 01:20:02,009
作为人质  他们对这个少校莱特有巨大的价值
They have tremendous value to this Major Wright, as hostages.

1016
01:20:02,179 --> 01:20:03,971
他会意识到这一点的
He will be aware of that.

1017
01:20:51,479 --> 01:20:53,886
鹰四狮一  请进来
Eagle Four to Lion One. Come in, please.

1018
01:20:56,108 --> 01:20:59,560
鹰四狮一  请进来
Eagle Four to Lion One. Come in, please.

1019
01:21:00,571 --> 01:21:05,067
我们可能离得太远了  我不知道他们能否再接我们
We may be too far away. I don't know if they can pick us up anymore.

1020
01:21:05,701 --> 01:21:08,157
鹰四狮一  请进来
Eagle Four to Lion One. Come in, please.

1021
01:21:08,329 --> 01:21:10,654
狮子一号到鹰四号  -你在吗
- Lion One to Eagle Four. - Are you there?

1022
01:21:10,831 --> 01:21:14,746
是的  我们在这里  718-9.
Yes, we are here. 7-187-9.

1023
01:21:14,919 --> 01:21:18,868
192724
192724.

1024
01:21:19,048 --> 01:21:21,087
