Give them these coordinates first.

1025
01:21:21,300 --> 01:21:25,594
告诉他们我想在1030的第二组坐标上集合
Tell them I want a rendezvous on the second set of coordinates at 1030.

1026
01:21:25,763 --> 01:21:32,097
我们正在南部通过4123-2179
We are proceeding south passing at 4123-2179.

1027
01:21:32,269 --> 01:21:36,563
你能安排在4128到2185与我们会合吗
Can you arrange a rendezvous with us at 4128-2185?

1028
01:21:36,732 --> 01:21:40,397
这会让我们做些什么  但是我们会试着在那里找到一个潜艇
It will tak e some doing, but we'll try to have one of our subs there.

1029
01:21:41,320 --> 01:21:43,277
你的ETA是多少
What is your ETA?

1030
01:21:43,447 --> 01:21:44,906
1030小时
1030 hours.

1031
01:21:45,074 --> 01:21:46,948
很好  再见
Very good. Cheerio.

1032
01:21:47,117 --> 01:21:48,861
干得好  Yelena
Good job, Yelena.

1033
01:21:49,036 --> 01:21:52,076
你知道  如果运气好的话  下星期我可以在伦敦给你买一杯饮料
You know, with any luck, I'll be able to buy you a drink in London next week.

1034
01:21:52,164 --> 01:21:54,536
在伦敦喝一杯真是太好了
It would be nice to have a drink in London.

1035
01:21:54,708 --> 01:21:56,831
自从蜜月以来我就没去过那儿
I haven't been there since my honeymoon.

1036
01:21:57,002 --> 01:21:59,920
好像是一千年前的事了  那是多久以前的事了
Seems like a thousand years ago. How long ago was it?

1037
01:22:00,089 --> 01:22:02,128
七年  你丈夫呢
Seven years. And your husband?

1038
01:22:02,758 --> 01:22:05,712
在战争的第一周被德国人杀害
Killed by the Germans in the first week of the war.

1039
01:22:06,762 --> 01:22:08,671
那么  你家里其他人呢
Well, how about the rest of your family?

1040
01:22:08,848 --> 01:22:10,390
他们中的一些人死了
Some of them are dead.

1041
01:22:10,558 --> 01:22:13,559
有些我不知道他们是死是活
Some I don't know if they're living or dead.

1042
01:22:14,145 --> 01:22:16,018
我哥哥  嗯…
My brother, well...

1043
01:22:16,188 --> 01:22:19,308
你知道我弟弟一定发生了什么事
You know what must have happened to my brother.

1044
01:22:22,278 --> 01:22:25,148
是的  我知道
Yes, I know.

1045
01:22:26,782 --> 01:22:28,775
好吧  你为什么不跟我们一起去呢
Well, look, why don't you come with us.

1046
01:22:28,951 --> 01:22:32,154
我的意思是  他们在伦敦流放了一个南斯拉夫政府
I mean, they got a Yugoslav government-in-exile in London.

1047
01:22:32,329 --> 01:22:34,322
你知道  他们会让你工作的
You know, they'll put you to work.

1048
01:22:34,498 --> 01:22:36,372
然后你可以在战后回来这里
And then you can come back here after the war.

1049
01:22:37,626 --> 01:22:41,494
当你这么说的时候  少校  我相信你最好相信它
When you say it, major, I believe lt. You better believe it.

1050
01:22:49,472 --> 01:22:52,840
嘿  少校  这些家伙大部分的英语说得比我好
Hey, major, most of these guys speak better English than I do.

1051
01:22:53,017 --> 01:22:56,765
是啊  别担心  看看他们发生了什么事
Yeah? Don't worry. Look what happened to them.

1052
01:23:07,907 --> 01:23:10,279
埃切瓦里  少校
Echevarria? Major.

1053
01:23:11,994 --> 01:23:13,785
你怎么样了  乔
And how you doing, Joe?

1054
01:23:13,954 --> 01:23:16,624
如果我有选择和你一起去Balkans旅游的话  少校
If I had my choice between touring the Balkans with you, major,

1055
01:23:16,790 --> 01:23:18,867
或者在巴黎经营一家夜总会
or running a nightclub in Paris,

1056
01:23:19,043 --> 01:23:20,241
叫我  Show Biz夜店先生
call me "Mr. Show Biz."

1057
01:23:20,419 --> 01:23:23,171
嗯  你会没事的
Hmm. You'll be all right.

1058
01:23:29,345 --> 01:23:33,888
好的  联系第十二亚历山大市的指挥官
All right, contact the commanding officer of the 12th at Alexandria.

1059
01:23:34,058 --> 01:23:37,391
告诉他立即对那列火车发动攻击
Tell him to execute an immediate attack on that train.

1060
01:23:37,561 --> 01:23:40,231
告诉他把它完全拿出来
Tell him to take it out completely.

1061
01:23:40,856 --> 01:23:42,813
杀死任何可见的东西
Kill anything in sight.

1062
01:23:43,442 --> 01:23:45,234
很好  先生
Very good, sir.

1063
01:23:46,070 --> 01:23:50,068
将军  你知道  我还不是莱特少校的崇拜者
General, as you know, I haven't been a great admirer of Major Wright,

1064
01:23:50,241 --> 01:23:52,814
但我相信他和他的部下有一个很好的尝试
but I'm sure he and his men had a damn good try.

1065
01:23:53,494 --> 01:23:55,570
哦  你真是太好了  上校
Well, that's damn nice of you, colonel.

1066
01:23:55,746 --> 01:23:57,573
但是时间是……对不起  将军
- But time is of... - Excuse me, general.

1067
01:23:57,748 --> 01:24:01,199
我们刚刚收到英国潜艇狮子一号的消息
We have just received word from the British submarine Lion One.

1068
01:24:01,877 --> 01:24:05,578
莱特少校袭击了保加利亚Sofia郊外的火车
Major Wright has attacked the train just outside of Sofia, Bulgaria,

1069
01:24:05,756 --> 01:24:07,713
在去爱琴海的路上
and is on his way to the Aegean.

1070
01:24:10,386 --> 01:24:12,295
好吧
All right!

1071
01:25:05,316 --> 01:25:08,151
你知道  少校  可能有12位高级党员
You know, major, there may be 12 high-ranking party members

1072
01:25:08,319 --> 01:25:10,146
或政府官员在那列火车上
or government officials upon that train.

1073
01:25:10,321 --> 01:25:11,352
是的  将军
Yes, general.

1074
01:25:11,530 --> 01:25:13,653
如果我呼吁停火和谈判
If I call for a cease-fire and negotiations,

1075
01:25:13,824 --> 01:25:16,315
在我发出命令之前  你不会采取任何行动
you will take no further actions until I give the command.

1076
01:25:16,494 --> 01:25:18,154
将军  我理解
I understand, general.

1077
01:25:19,121 --> 01:25:22,288
最重要的是  当然要拯救我们的人
The prime concern, of course, is to rescue our men.

1078
01:25:22,791 --> 01:25:24,583
第二个问题是确定
The second concern is to make sure

1079
01:25:24,752 --> 01:25:28,452
没有一个该死的美国人活着离开这里
that none of these damned Americans leave here alive.

1080
01:26:41,036 --> 01:26:42,744
他们在那儿  警官
There they are, sergeant.

1081
01:26:42,913 --> 01:26:44,372
All right, spread the word.

1082
01:26:44,540 --> 01:26:46,912
让所有人下车  前进  移动它
Get everybody off the train. Go ahead. Move it.

1083
01:26:47,084 --> 01:26:49,919
2420纳粹怎么样
What about the Nazis in 2420?

1084
01:26:50,588 --> 01:26:54,502
他们想要火车  我们要给他们
They wanted the train, we're gonna give it to them.

1085
01:27:05,811 --> 01:27:08,598
好吧  大家下车
All right, everybody out and off the train.

1086
01:27:12,860 --> 01:27:14,936
快点  跳下来
Come on, jump down!

1087
01:27:22,369 --> 01:27:24,362
开始射击
Commence firing!

1088
01:27:49,188 --> 01:27:51,145
走吧
Let's go!

1089
01:28:12,002 --> 01:28:14,244
好吧  Dravko  我们走吧
All right, Dravko, let's go.

1090
01:28:45,244 --> 01:28:47,486
把它们擦掉
Wipe them out!

1091
01:29:15,774 --> 01:29:17,814
去拿枪
Get to your gun!

1092
01:31:00,171 --> 01:31:03,088
我总是告诉你别紧张  肖蒂
I was always telling you to take it easy, Shorty.

1093
01:31:14,185 --> 01:31:15,560
好的  中士
All right, sergeant.

1094
01:31:15,728 --> 01:31:18,397
德国人将在15分钟内在这里增援
The Germans will have reinforcements here in 15 minutes.

1095
01:31:18,564 --> 01:31:21,850
让我们离开这里  和潜艇连接起来
Let's get out of here and link up with the sub.

1096
01:31:22,026 --> 01:31:24,018
我不和你一起去
I'm not going with you.

1097
01:31:24,195 --> 01:31:26,152
我不能  你在说什么
I can't. What are you talking about?

1098
01:31:26,322 --> 01:31:28,149
我的意思是  后面什么都没有
I mean, there's nothing for you back there.

1099
01:31:28,324 --> 01:31:29,569
哦  是的  有
Oh, yes, there is.

1100
01:31:29,742 --> 01:31:34,320
我给你走的每一个理由也是留下的理由
Every reason that I gave you to go is also a reason to stay.

1101
01:31:34,497 --> 01:31:39,538
我的丈夫  我的兄弟  我的整个家庭
My husband, my brother, my whole family.

1102
01:31:40,336 --> 01:31:42,375
同志们
My comrades.

1103
01:31:42,546 --> 01:31:45,333
我的生活就在这里  永远
My life is here, always.

1104
01:31:47,635 --> 01:31:49,711
你要去哪里  回到南斯拉夫
Where would you go? Back to Yugoslavia

1105
01:31:49,887 --> 01:31:51,678
加入蒂托的游击队
to join Tito's Partisans.

1106
01:31:54,266 --> 01:31:56,306
你会回来的
You will come back.

1107
01:31:58,896 --> 01:32:01,185
告诉我你会回来的
Tell me that you will come back.

1108
01:32:01,565 --> 01:32:02,846
该死的
Damn right.

1109
01:32:11,408 --> 01:32:13,401
让我们把它搬出去
Let's move it out.

1110
01:32:28,926 --> 01:32:31,334
我们走吧  士兵
Let's go, soldier!


